===Etymology===

From [[하늘]] (''ha.neul'', "heaven") + [[다람쥐]] (''da.ram.jwi'', "squirrel" or "chipmunk")

===Noun===

'''다람쥐''' (da.ram.jwi)

# [[flying squirrel]], especially the [[Siberian flying squirrel]], ''[[Pteromys volans]]''.

